name: Trap-Jaw Red Driver Ant
text:
2 Level 2 Insect monsters
If this card is Xyz Summoned: You can send 1 Insect monster from your Deck to the GY. You can detach 1 material from this card; Special Summon 1 "Trap-Jaw" monster from your hand, Deck, or GY. You can only activate this effect of "Trap-Jaw Red Driver Ant" once per turn.
